Class FinAckPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uci.iotproject.trafficreassembly.layer3.FinAckPair

  • public class FinAckPair
extends java.lang.Object
    Groups a FIN packet and its corresponding ACK packet. Immutable and thread safe.
